dataIdInfo.idPurp: Generate fishbones for address points and road centerlines using an existing streets address locator. The locator should be built from the road centerline feature class used for QAQC. If the road centerlines have a unique ID, that may be leveraged to relate the fishbones back to a specific ID. The locator must be built with this ID mapped to a field. Optionally filter fishbones based on the road's unique ID using the Apply Definition Query to Fishbones tool.
